                  <paragraph>Neurologic: Grossly nonfocal.</paragraph>
                  <paragraph>IMPRESSION:</paragraph>
                  <paragraph>1. Tachyarrhythmias.</paragraph>
                  <paragraph>2. Palpitations.</paragraph>
                  <paragraph>3. Chest pain.</paragraph>
