                  <paragraph>1. I have recommended Holter monitor for assessment of tachyarrhythmias.</paragraph>
                  <paragraph>2. The patient will also have stress test for evaluation of exercise-induced</paragraph>
                  <paragraph>arrhythmias.</paragraph>
